item.title: CoreUI PRO React.js Admin Template v5.0.0-rc.1 (CRA)
item.description: We are pleased to announce the release of CoreUI PRO React.js Admin Template v5.0.0-rc.1 (CRA) on March 22, 2024. This update brings a wealth of improvements and upgrades, ensuring that developers have access to the most advanced tools and features for building dynamic and responsive admin interfaces.
